verbose_text: MS data analysis revealed that this fraction mainly consists of GdSc 2 N@C 80 (I), Sc 3 N@C 78, and Gd 2 ScN@C 80 (I) (the ratio of the total ion currents corresponding to each molecule is 4:1.3:1, respectively), although trace amounts of Sc 3 N@C 80, Sc 4 C 2 @C 80 and GdSc 2 N@C 78 are also seen in the mass spectrum.
